snippet.title: Double Dodgers  - The Ultimate Multitasking Game - Trailer
snippet.description:
Play on Web: 
https://doubledodgers.com/
Available on the App Store: 
https://apps.apple.com/app/id1488942357
Available on Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=co.pelicanparty.doubledodgers

While walking home, you are playing a game on your phone. 
But don't get too fixated on the game or you'll walk into construction obstacles and you'll end up in the sewers. 

Test your reflexes and ability to multitask in this 2D & 3D dodging game. 
What's your high score?
